---
export const prerender = true;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SBTI 人格测试 - wordok.top</title>
  <meta name="description" content="SBTI 人格测试，31 题趣味人格画像，仅供娱乐。" />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://wordok.top/sbti/" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f3f4f9;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-hover: #f4f4f5;
      --text: #18181b;
      --text-secondary: #3f3f46;
      --muted: #52525b;
      --line: #e4e4e7;
      --soft: #f3f0ff;
      --accent: #6d28d9;
      --accent-hover: #5b21b6;
      --accent-muted: #7c3aed;
      --accent-border: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.35);
      --gradient: linear-gradient(120deg, #5b21b6 0%, #0891b2 100%);
      --shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.09);
      --shadow-sm: 0 4px 16px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-panel: 22px;
      --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root {
        --bg: #09090b;
        --surface: #18181b;
        --surface-hover: #27272a;
        --text: #fafafa;
        --text-secondary: #e4e4e7;
        --muted: #d4d4d8;
        --line: #3f3f46;
        --soft: #27272a;
        --accent: #a78bfa;
        --accent-hover: #c4b5fd;
        --accent-muted: #c4b5fd;
        --accent-border: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.45);
        --gradient: linear-gradient(120deg, #a78bfa 0%, #22d3ee 100%);
        --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        --shadow-sm: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      }
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; scroll-padding-top: 88px; }
    body {
      font-family: var(--font);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 0% 0%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.14) 0%, transparent 52%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 100% 8%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.10) 0%, transparent 48%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.06) 0%, transparent 55%);
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      body {
        background-image:
          radial-gradient(ellipse 120% 80% at 0% 0%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.12) 0%, transparent 52%),
          radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 100% 8%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.08) 0%, transparent 48%),
          radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 100%, rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.15) 0%, transparent 55%);
      }
    }
    .shell { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 18px 48px; }
    .page-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      padding-bottom: 18px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 85%, transparent);
    }
    .brand-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: var(--surface);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      transition: background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .brand-link:hover { background: var(--surface-hover); border-color: var(--accent-border); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
    .page-title {
      font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 28px);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      background: var(--gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    /* 参考 unun：大卡片 + 角上柔光 */
    .panel {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 90%, var(--accent) 4%);
      border-radius: var(--radius-panel);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 26px 24px 28px;
    }
    .panel::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: -72px;
      top: -56px;
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(165deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 22%, transparent), color-mix(in srgb, #0891b2 18%, transparent));
      opacity: 0.45;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .panel > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .panel::after { opacity: 0.28; }
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-muted);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 88%, var(--surface)), var(--surface));
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .intro-banner {
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 20px 20px 20px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(125deg, var(--surface) 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 65%, var(--surface)) 45%, color-mix(in srgb, #ecfeff 40%, var(--surface)) 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .intro-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(125deg, var(--surface) 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 70%, #312e81) 50%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 75%, #164e63) 100%);
        box-shadow: none;
      }
    }
    .intro-banner p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.78; }
    .intro-banner strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }
    .progress-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 93%, transparent);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 12px 4px 14px;
      margin-left: -4px;
      margin-right: -4px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 75%, transparent);
    }
    .progress {
      flex: 1;
      height: 10px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 85%, var(--soft));
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .progress span {
      display: block;
      height: 100%;
      width: 0;
      background: var(--gradient);
      border-radius: inherit;
      transition: width 0.28s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 35%, transparent);
    }
    .progress-text { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .question-list { display: grid; gap: 18px; min-height: 80px; }
    .question-list .quiz-loading { margin: 0; padding: 36px 12px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .question {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 88%, var(--accent) 6%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 45%, var(--surface)) 0%, var(--surface) 38%, color-mix(in srgb, #ecfeff 22%, var(--surface)) 100%);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .question {
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 88%, #312e81) 0%, var(--surface) 45%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 90%, #164e63) 100%);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      }
    }
    .question::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 4px;
      border-radius: var(--radius) 0 0 var(--radius);
      background: var(--gradient);
      opacity: 0.85;
    }
    .question-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      padding: 14px 16px 12px 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 80%, transparent);
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 65%, transparent);
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--soft), color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 70%, var(--surface)));
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 75%, var(--accent) 12%);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--accent);
    }
    .question-dim {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 70%, var(--surface));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .question-stem {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 3.25rem 1fr;
      gap: 12px 14px;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 16px 16px 18px 18px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .question-stem { grid-template-columns: 2.75rem 1fr; padding-left: 16px; }
    }
    .question-index {
      font-size: clamp(26px, 6vw, 32px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      background: linear-gradient(165deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 42%, var(--line)), color-mix(in srgb, #0891b2 35%, var(--line)));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      user-select: none;
      padding-top: 2px;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .question-index {
        background: linear-gradient(165deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 55%, var(--muted)), color-mix(in srgb, #22d3ee 40%, var(--muted)));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
      }
    }
    .question-title-wrap { min-width: 0; }
    .question-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .options {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
      padding: 0 14px 16px 18px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .options-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding-top: 4px;
    }
    .options-head-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gradient);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 18%, transparent);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .options-head-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    /* 单选 · 字母键帽 · 文案 */
    .option {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 20px auto 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      column-gap: 12px;
      row-gap: 6px;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff, color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 55%, #ffffff));
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color 0.16s ease, background 0.16s ease, box-shadow 0.16s ease, transform 0.16s ease;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .option {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 92%, var(--bg)), var(--surface));
      }
    }
    .option:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .option:hover {
      border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 45%, var(--line));
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 40%, var(--surface)), color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 25%, var(--surface)));
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.08);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .option:focus-within {
      outline: 2px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 38%, transparent);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .option:has(input:checked) {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 75%, var(--surface)), color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 45%, var(--surface)));
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--accent-border), 0 4px 18px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.12);
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .option:has(input:checked) .option-key {
      background: var(--gradient);
      border-color: transparent;
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.25);
    }
    .option:has(input:checked) .option-code { color: #fff; -webkit-text-fill-color: #fff; }
    .option input {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      accent-color: var(--accent);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .option-key {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 2.25rem;
      height: 2.25rem;
      margin-top: 4px;
      padding: 0 8px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 70%, var(--accent) 15%);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 80%, var(--surface)), var(--surface));
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      transition: background 0.16s ease, border-color 0.16s ease, box-shadow 0.16s ease, color 0.16s ease;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .option-key {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface-hover), var(--surface));
        box-shadow: none;
      }
    }
    .option-code {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .option-text {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.68;
      min-width: 0;
      padding-top: 6px;
    }
    .actions-bar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding-top: 22px;
      border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 88%, transparent);
    }
    .hint { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.65; flex: 1; min-width: 200px; }
    .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    button {
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font: inherit;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      transition: transform 0.16s ease, opacity 0.15s, background 0.15s, box-shadow 0.16s ease;
    }
    button:hover:not(:disabled) { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    button:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.28);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.32); }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: var(--surface);
      color: var(--accent);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--surface-hover); border-color: var(--accent-border); }
    .screen { display: none; }
    .screen.active { display: block; }
    .result-panel { padding: 28px 26px 30px; }
    .panel .result-wrap {
      background: transparent;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .result-layout { display: grid; gap: 22px; }
    .result-top { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 20px; align-items: stretch; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .result-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .poster-box, .type-box, .analysis-box, .dim-box, .note-box {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--surface) 0%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 40%, var(--surface)) 100%);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .poster-box {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 200px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .poster-box::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 90% 12%, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 12%, transparent), transparent 42%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .poster-box > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .poster-box.no-image .poster-image { display: none; }
    .poster-image { width: 100%; max-height: 300px; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 50%, transparent); }
    .poster-caption { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; margin-top: auto; }
    .type-kicker { font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent-muted); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .type-name {
      font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      background: var(--gradient);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .type-subname { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.65; }
    .match {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--soft), color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 70%, var(--surface)));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .analysis-box h3, .dim-box h3, .note-box h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 85%, var(--accent) 8%);
    }
    .analysis-box p, .note-box p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.85; white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0; }
    .dim-list { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .dim-item {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) inset;
    }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .dim-item { box-shadow: none; }
    }
    .dim-item-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .dim-item-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .dim-item-score { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; }
    .dim-item p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }
    .author-box {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--soft) 30%, var(--surface)), var(--surface));
    }
    .author-box summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .author-box summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .author-box summary::after {
      content: '展开';
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }
    .author-box[open] summary::after { content: '收起'; }
    .author-content { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 16px 18px 18px; }
    .author-content p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.85; margin: 10px 0 0; }
    .author-content p:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
    .result-actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--line) 88%, transparent);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn-link {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 14px 22px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      transition: background 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.22);
    }
    .btn-link:hover { background: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(91, 33, 182, 0.28); }
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .shell { padding: 18px 14px 40px; }
      .panel { padding: 22px 18px 24px; }
      .panel::after { width: 140px; height: 140px; right: -48px; top: -44px; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
      .option:hover, .option:has(input:checked), button:hover:not(:disabled) { transform: none; }
      .progress span { transition: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <header class="page-header">
      <a class="brand-link" href="/">← wordok.top</a>
      <h1 class="page-title">SBTI 人格测试</h1>
    </header>
    <section id="test" class="screen active">
      <div class="panel test-panel">
        <span class="eyebrow">wordok · 31 题 · 仅供娱乐</span>
        <div class="intro-banner">
          <p><strong>MBTI 已经过时，SBTI 来了。</strong> 共 31 道题，全部选完后即可查看你的人格画像。本测试仅供娱乐，别太当真。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-wrap">
          <div class="progress"><span id="progressBar"></span></div>
          <div class="progress-text" id="progressText">0 / 31</div>
        </div>
        <div id="questionList" class="question-list">
          <p class="quiz-loading">题目加载中…</p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions-bar">
          <div class="hint" id="testHint">全选完才会放行。</div>
          <div class="btn-group">
            <button id="submitBtn" class="btn-primary" disabled>提交并查看结果</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="result" class="screen">
      <div class="panel result-panel">
        <div class="result-wrap">
        <div class="result-layout">
          <div class="result-top">
            <div class="poster-box" id="posterBox">
              <img id="posterImage" class="poster-image" alt="人格结果图" />
              <div id="posterCaption" class="poster-caption"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="type-box">
              <div class="type-kicker" id="resultModeKicker">你的主类型</div>
              <div class="type-name" id="resultTypeName"></div>
              <div class="match" id="matchBadge"></div>
              <div class="type-subname" id="resultTypeSub"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="analysis-box">
            <h3>人格解读</h3>
            <p id="resultDesc"></p>
          </div>
          <div class="dim-box">
            <h3>十五维度评分</h3>
            <div id="dimList" class="dim-list"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="note-box">
            <h3>友情提示</h3>
            <p id="funNote"></p>
          </div>
          <details class="author-box">
            <summary>作者的话</summary>
            <div class="author-content">
              <p>本测试首发于 B 站 up 主蛆肉儿串儿（UID417038183），初衷是劝诫一位爱喝酒的朋友戒酒。</p>
              <p>由于作者的人格是 SHIT 愤世者，所以平等地攻击了各位，在此抱歉！不过我是一个绝世大美女，你们一定会原谅我。</p>
              <p>关于这个测试，我没法很好地平衡娱乐和专业性，因此对于一些人格的阐释较为模糊或完全不准，如有冒犯非常抱歉！</p>
              <p>总之好玩为主，还请不要用于盈利。</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
        <div class="result-actions">
          <button id="restartBtn" class="btn-secondary">重新测试</button>
          <a href="/" class="btn-link">返回 wordok 首页</a>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <script is:inline src="/sbti/main.js"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    (function(){ if(typeof startTest==='function') startTest(false); })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
